CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 17, 1970, pg. 6, reads: "Church Leaders Celebrate - The exclusive dining area at the Top of The Towers was the scene of the Pre Christmas Dinner Party given by the Baptist Ministers and their wives recently...Representatives of the official family of the Allegheny Union Baptist Association in top right photo are, Mrs. J. C. Hairston, Rev. J. O. Neal, moderator, Lower Monongahela Area; Mrs. Neal, Rev. J. A. Williams, AUBA Moderator, Mrs. Williams, Rev. E. D. Davis, moderator Upper Monongahela Area, Mrs. Davis and Mrs. Alfred L. Pugh. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mrs. J. C. Hairston, Rev. J. O. Neal, Mrs. Neal, Rev. J. A. Williams, Mrs. Williams, Rev. E. D. Davis, Mrs. Davis, and Mrs. Alfred L. Pugh, at Baptist Ministers pre-Christmas dinner, Top of the Towers restaurant
